{
  "texts": [
    "Appropriately asked, LLMs might be powerful internal search engines & content providers.",
    "Automation of often asked questions about HR, IT, or banking policies has a pragmatic use.",
    "Workers could ask the system questions such as, \"How many days of leave may I defer?\"",
    "or \"What is the procedure for reporting insider trading issues?\"",
    "instead of relying on a specific document."
  ]
}